{"tid":2329419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾任恐怖組織首腦？美經濟學家控訴譚德塞涉「種族滅絕罪」","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:22:27.000Z","uid":53379,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93c6f0f414335cd75891db7cc9b866cba66071e6","tid":2329419,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">曾任恐怖組織首腦？美經濟學家控訴譚德塞涉「種族滅絕罪」</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/15/phpn1jpEr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F15%2Fphpn1jpEr.jpg&h=065bdf0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWHO秘書長譚德塞被指控曾擔任過具有共產黨背景的「泰格瑞省人民解放陣線」領袖，涉犯下種族滅絕罪。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕衣索比亞籍的世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）遭指控協助衣國反政府組織「泰格瑞省人民解放陣線」（Tigray People's Liberation Front, TPLF）發動內戰，現更被美國經濟學家爆料曾擔任該組織首腦，已向國際刑事法院（ICC）控訴譚犯下「種族滅絕罪」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《泰晤士報》報導，曾獲得諾貝爾和平獎提名的美國經濟學家斯坦曼（David Steinman）指控，WHO秘書長譚德塞擔任過具有共產黨背景的「泰格瑞省人民解放陣線」領袖，該組織已被美國政府列為全球恐怖組織，涉嫌在當地強占土地、濫殺異見者。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3382032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3382032&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28dToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=29314671\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3382032&h=7901dab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3382032</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/who-chief-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-may-face-genocide-charges-2fbfz7sff\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fwho-chief-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-may-face-genocide-charges-2fbfz7sff&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28dToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=06e0ce35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/who-chief-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-may-face-genocide-charges-2fbfz7sff</a>"},{"pid":"99e27b78e61df2e2a6f90101b152deaf3e57b953","tid":2329419,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46178b3abe565c608d07391bd6c3eccc77187d2","tid":2329419,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5db0af6bc1fc945dd469b9185c1e33303078e53b","tid":2329419,"uid":357781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"新聞？1月已經知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f628652a7d2fa66662cca9f17b22432afd4586","tid":2329419,"uid":298796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5db0af6bc1fc945dd469b9185c1e33303078e53b","tid":2329419,"uid":357781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"新聞？1月已經知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:22:27.000Z","msg":"係呀, 一月已經知道<br />\n不過而家告都無用, 左媒唔同你報, 告左等於無告"}]}